review_blob: Excellent, excellent beer.  Wonderful, subtle chocolate flavor, smooth and highly drinkable.  An awesome winter/fall beer.
Incredibly complex flavor.  I couldnt even begin to describe it with my limited vocabulary.
Nice, creamy stout.  I enjoyed it - the color was dark, but I would have liked it to be a bit darker.
Nice bitter hoppy taste, and I love the ridiculous carbonation.
